tory, star study, and memoir, Bette Davis Black and White allows us to contemplate cross-racial spectatorship in new ways.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aAfrican American motion picture actors and actresseszUnited States. 0aAfrican Americans in motion pictures. 0aAfrican Americans in the motion picture industryzUnited States. 0aMotion picture actors and actresseszUnited States. 0aRace in motion pictures. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073919040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226813721423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226813721/original  a978-3-11-073919-0  University of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles